				\begin{document}$\hat {\lambda }=0$\end{document}λ^=0. Next consider a trial where observed xi values are uniform on (0,1) or (0.5,1.5), also depicted by grey horizontal bars in Fig. 1. It is now clear that when the analyst fits their model (2), \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
